 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;"> kicked him off</a>.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: =
5px;">The investors have no power over the board: They had no voting rights=
 at all, and OpenAI <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
k/33944330.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzL=
