<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The problem is that the startups really do wan=
t those lists to be secret, and they will be mad if you go and use them to =
broker trades. And Carta did that: It came to a shareholder of a company wh=
ose cap table it manages, pitching that shareholder on selling his stock; t=
he shareholder told the company and the company complained. And the result =
is that Carta is shutting down its brokerage business.=C2=A0<a href=3D"http=
