<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/33944330.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMDMvaW5zaWRlci10cmFkaW5nLWlzLWJldHRlci1mcm9tLWhvbWU_=
Y21waWQ9QkJEMDEwOTI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5=
ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjQwMTA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07cee=
f4b8524a319a23cBa3446f08" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" ta=
rget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; =
border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style=
: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked last June</a> about how the Covi=
d-19 pandemic, and the associated rise in working from home, was good for w=
ork-from-home insider trading. Some percentage of insider trading involves =
people overhearing their partners=E2=80=99 work calls at home, or looking a=
t their partners=E2=80=99 work email while their partners are in the bathro=
om, and then trading on the partners=E2=80=99 work information. If everyone=
 works from the office, there is a limited opportunity for this sort of thi=
ng. If everyone works from the bedroom they share with their partner, there=
 is tons of opportunity for this sort of thing.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Today there=E2=80=99s a <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33944330.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNv=
bS9maW5hbmNlL2luc2lkZXItdHJhZGluZy1waWxsb3ctdGFsay13b3JrLWZyb20taG9tZS1hNTZ=
lMjg0OD9tb2Q9aHBfZmVhdHN0X3BvczU/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB88f40515" itempro=
p=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #=
000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-=
bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"=
> Wall Street Journal A-hed treatment</a> of the trend:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a rich history in securities fraud of=
 =E2=80=9Cpillow talk=E2=80=9D cases, in which insider traders glean confid=
ential information from romantic partners. The Covid era offered a twist: S=
ecrets weren=E2=80=99t spilled in the bedroom or over a bottle of wine, but=
 during the humdrum routine of two adults working from home.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDuring Covid, there was an uptick in =
brazen conduct,=E2=80=9D said Edward Imperatore, a defense lawyer at law fi=
rm Morrison &amp; Foerster. =E2=80=9CIn a work-from-home environment, peopl=
e acted with more impunity.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That strikes me as an obviously wrong analysis=
? It=E2=80=99s not that people =E2=80=9Cacted with more impunity,=E2=80=9D =
that they always had access to their partners=E2=80=99 inside information b=
ut became lawless monster during Covid. It=E2=80=99s that people had way, w=
ay, way, way, way more <em>opportunity=C2=A0</em>to access their partners=
=E2=80=99 inside information, and the brazen ones made use of it.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The legal problem in these cases is: Did the i=
nsider=C2=A0<em>tip=C2=A0</em>her partner,=C2=A0<em>hoping=C2=A0</em>that h=
e would trade on her work information, or did the partner=C2=A0<em>betray=
=C2=A0</em>the insider, stealing her information while she wasn=E2=80=99t l=
ooking and selfishly jeopardizing her career so he could make a little mone=
y?<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" style=3D"color: #000000;=
 text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-=
color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: tra=
nsparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a>=C2=A0I think the answer is usually the latter, but not always:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One challenge for prosecutors is determining w=
hether the partner who is privy to the information was in on the crime, sai=
d former federal prosecutor Brendan Quigley.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDo they say, =E2=80=98Oh, my God, I w=
ould never give information to my spouse or significant other?=E2=80=99 It =
depends not only on what actually happened, but also on the nature of their=
 relationship,=E2=80=9D said Quigley, who prosecuted insider-trading cases =
in Manhattan.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For defense lawyers, pillow-talk cases can be =
difficult to handle at trial, particularly if one partner testifies against=
 another. =E2=80=9CTo a juror, this is the bad boyfriend,=E2=80=9D said Imp=
eratore, the defense attorney. =E2=80=9CHe=E2=80=99s acting badly in a rela=
tionship in a way that goes beyond the four corners of insider trading.=E2=
=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Not surprisingly, many such relationships don=
=E2=80=99t survive.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/33944330.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS92aWV3=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTQtMDgtMTgvb25lLWdvbGYtY291cnNlLXRoYXQtcy1ncmVhdC1mb3Itc3R=
vY2stdGlwcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTA5MjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV=
9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAxMDkmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1Z=
mY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa6cfe5b0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked about this problem</=
a> in the case of golf buddies: Sometimes, corporate executives talk about =
their work on the golf course, treating golf like therapy and expecting the=
ir golf buddies to keep it confidential. (In that case, if the golf buddy t=
rades, he is guilty of insider trading, but the executive isn=E2=80=99t.)=
=C2=A0Other times, corporate executives talk about their work on the golf c=
ourse=C2=A0<em>in order to tip their golf buddies</em>, expecting those bud=
dies to go trade on it. (In that case, they=E2=80=99re both guilty of insid=
er trading.)=C2=A0If you=E2=80=99re not playing the round with them, it is =
hard to know which cases are which. Same, but more so, with romantic partne=
rs.</p>
